# Team Certification Performance Patterns (Synthetic)

## Key Insights from Historical Data

- Teams with **weekly study hours > 8** show 35% higher pass rates
- Engineers with **< 15 meeting hours/week** complete certifications 2x faster
- Practice test scores **> 80%** correlate strongly with actual exam success
- Morning study sessions (6-9 AM) show 22% higher retention than evening sessions

## Recommended Team Practices
- Block 2 focused hours per week per team member
- Run bi-weekly practice tests as a team
- Use Microsoft Learn Sandbox for hands-on labs